# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:14
translate spanish mari2_cfee0164:

    # fr "Hey honey, how are you doing today?"
    fr "Hola, cariño, ¿cómo estás hoy?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:15
translate spanish mari2_b25a5732:

    # "She looks like she isn't in a great mood today. Not her normal flirty self."
    "Parece que hoy no está de muy buen humor. No es la misma coqueta de siempre."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:18
translate spanish mari2_8bbaf6cc:

    # fr "Good. Let me know if you need anything."
    fr "Bien. Dime si necesitas algo."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:22
translate spanish mari2_eaf17857:

    # fr "Oh I'm okay. Thanks for asking though."
    fr "Oh, estoy bien. Pero gracias por preguntar."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:23
translate spanish mari2_7d52d223:

    # fr "Let me know if you need anything."
    fr "Dime si necesitas algo."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:26
translate spanish mari2_2d8fae6e:

    # "She goes off to help other customers and I finish my meal."
    "Ella se va a atender a otros clientes y yo termino mi comida."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:27
translate spanish mari2_89a46191:

    # "When I get up to put a tip on the table and leave, she walks back over to me."
    "Cuando me levanto para dejar una propina en la mesa y marcharme, ella vuelve hacia mí."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:32
translate spanish mari2_88c41b9d:

    # fr "Hey, could I ask a favor of you?"
    fr "Oye, ¿te puedo pedir un favor?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:33
translate spanish mari2_82701f42:

    # pc "Sure, what's up?"
    pc "Claro, ¿qué pasa?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:34
translate spanish mari2_213affe7:

    # fr "Could you give me a ride home? My ride sort of flaked on me and I don't have any other way."
    fr "¿Me podrías llevar a casa? El que me iba a recoger me ha dejado tirada y no tengo otra forma de llegar."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:40
translate spanish mari2_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/mari_thankyousomuch.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_thankyousomuch.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:41
translate spanish mari2_eb69738f:

    # fr "Oh my God, thank you so much."
    fr "Dios mío, muchísimas gracias."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:42
translate spanish mari2_2adb5a8d:

    # fr "Give me just a second and I'll get my things."
    fr "Dame un segundo y voy a por mis cosas."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:46
translate spanish mari2_0d357970:

    # fr "Oh, I can give you gas money, that's not a problem."
    fr "Ah, te puedo dar dinero para la gasolina, no hay problema."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:49
translate spanish mari2_62b6a0da:

    # "She pulls $10 out of her roll of tips and hands it to me."
    "Saca 10 dólares de su rollo de propinas y me los da."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:50
translate spanish mari2_f974fab7:

    # fr "Is that good?"
    fr "¿Te vale?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:51
translate spanish mari2_0b6a83d2:

    # pc "It'll do."
    pc "Me vale."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:54
translate spanish mari2_3438dbc6:

    # fr "Great. Give me just a second and I'll get my things."
    fr "Genial. Dame un segundo y voy a por mis cosas."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:59
translate spanish mari2_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/mari_really.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_really.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:60
translate spanish mari2_4d187fb5:

    # fr "Really? That's all you're interested in?"
    fr "¿En serio? ¿Eso es lo único que te interesa?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:61
translate spanish mari2_43e318dc:

    # fr "I mean, maybe we'll get there eventually, but I'm not going to pay you for a ride with sex."
    fr "Quiero decir, quizá lleguemos a eso al final, pero no voy a pagarte el viaje a cambio de sexo."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:62
translate spanish mari2_78bddb29:

    # fr "I'm not a fucking hooker, and if that's all you're interested in, you're going to be real disappointed."
    fr "No soy una puta de mierda, y si eso es lo único que te interesa, te vas a llevar una gran decepción."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:63
translate spanish mari2_f12af312:

    # fr "I thought you were a good guy."
    fr "Pensaba que eras un buen tipo."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:64
translate spanish mari2_a2c38898:

    # pc "I'm sorry, you're right. I didn't mean to offend you."
    pc "Lo siento, tienes razón. No quería ofenderte."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:65
translate spanish mari2_4d330eb0:

    # fr "It's fine. I'll find somebody else to give me a ride."
    fr "No pasa nada. Encontraré a otra persona que me lleve."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:66
translate spanish mari2_c4ac6d6e:

    # pc "No really, I'm sorry. I'll give you a ride, it's no problem."
    pc "No, en serio, lo siento. Te llevaré yo, no hay problema."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:67
translate spanish mari2_67fd9cd9:

    # fr "Really?"
    fr "¿En serio?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:68
translate spanish mari2_b65a9522:

    # pc "Yeah. Seriously. I'm sorry."
    pc "Sí. De verdad. Lo siento."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:71
translate spanish mari2_99a094ef:

    # fr "Alright then, you're forgiven. Give me just a second and I'll go get my things."
    fr "Vale, entonces te perdono. Dame un segundo y voy a por mis cosas."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:74
translate spanish mari2_b5cd2a72:

    # "She walks to the back and returns a few minutes later."
    "Se dirige hacia la parte de atrás y vuelve unos minutos más tarde."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:75
translate spanish mari2_d71a2aa1:

    # "Jackson stops her with a hand on her shoulder."
    "Jackson la detiene poniéndole una mano en el hombro."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:79
translate spanish mari2_531c37ba:

    # jk "You gonna be okay, honey?"
    jk "¿Vas a estar bien, cariño?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:80
translate spanish mari2_a6099dab:

    # fr "Yeah, he's going to give me a ride home."
    fr "Sí, él me va a llevar a casa."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:81
translate spanish mari2_8173ea67:

    # "Jackson looks at me as if he is memorizing every feature of my face."
    "Jackson me mira como si estuviera memorizando cada rasgo de mi rostro."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:82
translate spanish mari2_6488aae0:

    # jk "Alright, you just be careful."
    jk "De acuerdo, ten cuidado."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:83
translate spanish mari2_3d89522a:

    # fr "I will. See you tomorrow."
    fr "Lo haré. Nos vemos mañana."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:84
translate spanish mari2_305b4486:

    # "With that, she gives him a quick hug and then walks over to meet me at the front door."
    "Dicho esto, le da un rápido abrazo y luego se acerca a la puerta principal para reunirse conmigo."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:88
translate spanish mari2_9e7f945c:

    # fr "Ready."
    fr "Lista."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:89
translate spanish mari2_70536ac6:

    # pc "Alright, let's go."
    pc "Vale, vamos."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:94
translate spanish mari2_1c8790ac:

    # "I lead her out to the car and we get in and start down the road."
    "La acompaño hasta el coche, nos subimos y echamos a la carretera."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:95
translate spanish mari2_de1f8e81:

    # fr "My place is a little out of town on Highway 69."
    fr "Mi casa está un poco a las afueras, en la autopista 69."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:96
translate spanish mari2_f3f37acf:

    # fr "If you just follow this road for a while, I'll tell you where to turn."
    fr "Si sigues por esta carretera un rato, te diré dónde girar."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:97
translate spanish mari2_cd58ed18:

    # fr "I'm sorry I didn't tell you how far out it was. I figured that once I got in the car, you wouldn't kick me out."
    fr "Siento no haberte dicho lo lejos que estaba. Pensé que, una vez en el coche, no me echarías."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:100
translate spanish mari2_76bd5ac0:

    # fr "Yeah, I'm sorry. You're not going to kick me out are you?"
    fr "Sí, lo siento. No vas a echarme, ¿verdad?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:101
translate spanish mari2_244880a1:

    # pc "Not this time."
    pc "Esta vez no."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:102
translate spanish mari2_da9fa5f9:

    # fr "Phew!"
    fr "¡Uf!"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:104
translate spanish mari2_c982865c:

    # fr "Well that's nice to hear."
    fr "Me alegro de oírlo."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:105
translate spanish mari2_2ee8f7d9:

    # fr "I honestly don't know what I would have done if you hadn't given me a ride."
    fr "Sinceramente, no sé qué habría hecho si no me hubieras dado un paseo."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:106
translate spanish mari2_ea4aaa45:

    # fr "Jackson doesn't drive anymore and he lives right next to the restaurant and Connie flaked out on me."
    fr "Jackson ya no conduce y vive justo al lado del restaurante, y Connie me dejó tirada."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:107
translate spanish mari2_5e87a42c:

    # pc "You don't have any other friends?"
    pc "¿No tienes otros amigos?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:110
translate spanish mari2_37eecf83:

    # fr "Not really. I work pretty much every night and go to school during the day."
    fr "La verdad es que no. Trabajo casi todas las noches y voy a la escuela durante el día."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:111
translate spanish mari2_be893470:

    # pc "You're going to college?"
    pc "¿Vas a la universidad?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:115
translate spanish mari2_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice 'voices/mari_yeah.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_yeah.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:116
translate spanish mari2_2b133d9a:

    # fr "Yeah, I mean I like working for Jackson, but I don't want to be a waitress all my life."
    fr "Sí, bueno, me gusta trabajar para Jackson, pero no quiero ser camarera toda mi vida."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:117
translate spanish mari2_764b7928:

    # pc "You go to Skyhill?"
    pc "¿Vas a Skyhill?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:118
translate spanish mari2_b9bbe0c8:

    # fr "No I'm in the veterinarian program in Whiterock."
    fr "No, estoy en el programa de veterinaria en Whiterock."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:119
translate spanish mari2_d9c0d3c2:

    # pc "Veterinarian? That's cool."
    pc "¿Veterinaria? Qué guay."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:120
translate spanish mari2_95ddebf0:

    # fr "Yeah, I love animals. I volunteer at the Skyhill Animal clinic on the weekend too."
    fr "Sí, me encantan los animales. También soy voluntaria en la clínica veterinaria de Skyhill los fines de semana."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:121
translate spanish mari2_9f24bfc7:

    # fr "And then when I'm not doing all of that, I have to take care of the farm, so not a lot of time for friends."
    fr "Y cuando no estoy haciendo todo eso, tengo que ocuparme de la granja, así que no me queda mucho tiempo para los amigos."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:122
translate spanish mari2_b7bcaa75:

    # pc "Farm?"
    pc "¿Granja?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:123
translate spanish mari2_34b74c62:

    # fr "Yeah, I live on a farm. You'll see. It's coming up here on the right."
    fr "Sí, vivo en una granja. Ya lo verás. Está justo aquí, a la derecha."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:126
translate spanish mari2_176d45b6:

    # fr "You're gonna want to slow down a bit. The turn is real easy to miss."
    fr "Será mejor que reduzcas un poco la velocidad. Es muy fácil pasarse el desvío."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:127
translate spanish mari2_57fbb466:

    # fr "Right there, behind those trees, see the mailbox?"
    fr "Justo ahí, detrás de esos árboles, ¿ves el buzón?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:128
translate spanish mari2_4fe57c0e:

    # pc "Yeah, I see it."
    pc "Sí, lo veo."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:131
translate spanish mari2_baf3d043:

    # "I take a right onto a narrow dirt road that leads into the woods, then the woods clear away to reveal Mari's farm."
    "Giro a la derecha por un estrecho camino de tierra que se adentra en el bosque, y luego el bosque se abre para revelar la granja de Mari."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:134
translate spanish mari2_0d086ddf:

    # "There are fields of crops, a barn with livestock, and an old farmhouse that looks much too big for a single person."
    "Hay campos de cultivo, un granero con ganado y una vieja casa de campo que parece demasiado grande para una sola persona."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:135
translate spanish mari2_0ea772b8:

    # pc "You live here by yourself?"
    pc "¿Vives aquí sola?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:137
translate spanish mari2_d41d8cd9_3:

    # voice 'voices/mari_yep.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_yep.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:138
translate spanish mari2_15e9c674:

    # fr "Yep, I run the whole operation."
    fr "Sí, me encargo de todo el negocio."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:139
translate spanish mari2_4b1a346a:

    # pc "Wow. I'm impressed."
    pc "Vaya. Estoy impresionado."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:140
translate spanish mari2_8fc70d8d:

    # fr "Thanks. It's hard work, but I love it."
    fr "Gracias. Es un trabajo duro, pero me encanta."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:141
translate spanish mari2_5679a178:

    # fr "Maybe you could come out during the day sometime and see the animals. I could always use a hand on the weekends."
    fr "Quizá podrías venir algún día durante el día a ver a los animales. Siempre me viene bien una mano los fines de semana."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:142
translate spanish mari2_919834dc:

    # pc "I might take you up on that."
    pc "Puede que te haga caso."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:147
translate spanish mari2_4ac7c9d1:

    # fr "Well thanks for the ride. I really appreciate it."
    fr "Bueno, gracias por traerme. Te lo agradezco mucho."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:148
translate spanish mari2_0144fcab:

    # pc "It's no problem."
    pc "No hay problema."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:149
translate spanish mari2_74dad108:

    # fr "You remember how to get back?"
    fr "¿Te acuerdas de cómo volver?"

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:150
translate spanish mari2_560198a5:

    # pc "Yeah, I can manage."
    pc "Sí, me las arreglaré."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:151
translate spanish mari2_0f1224ae:

    # fr "All right, well I better get in. Got another busy day tomorrow."
    fr "Muy bien, pues mejor me voy. Mañana me espera otro día ajetreado."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:152
translate spanish mari2_859bb5e6:

    # "She takes off her seat belt, then quickly leans over and kisses me on the cheek."
    "Se quita el cinturón de seguridad, luego se inclina rápidamente y me da un beso en la mejilla."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:155
translate spanish mari2_35b4ee40:

    # fr "Thanks again, you're the best."
    fr "Gracias de nuevo, eres el mejor."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:157
translate spanish mari2_d41d8cd9_4:

    # voice 'voices/mari_goodnight2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mari_goodnight2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:158
translate spanish mari2_aa3809b0:

    # fr "Good night."
    fr "Buenas noches."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:161
translate spanish mari2_f4ea6f40:

    # "With that, she gets out of the car and starts up towards her front porch."
    "Dicho esto, sale del coche y se dirige hacia el porche de su casa."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:162
translate spanish mari2_0b673066:

    # "I wait until she gets her front door open and disappears inside before turning around and driving out of her farm and back onto the highway."
    "Espero a que abra la puerta principal y desaparezca dentro antes de dar media vuelta y salir de su granja para volver a la autopista."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:167
translate spanish mari2_c755bc5c:

    # "She always seems like she is so happy, but I feel like there is a sort of sadness hidden under that cheer."
    "Siempre parece tan feliz, pero tengo la sensación de que hay una especie de tristeza escondida bajo esa alegría."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:168
translate spanish mari2_e75e84b3:

    # "I wonder why she is living on that big farm all by herself."
    "Me pregunto por qué vive sola en esa gran granja."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:169
translate spanish mari2_efa9db91:

    # "I'll have to ask her sometime. I'd love to learn more about her."
    "Tendré que preguntárselo algún día. Me encantaría saber más sobre ella."

# game/Scenes/Mari/mari2.rpy:170
translate spanish mari2_5cb073e5:

    # "The kiss had been nice too."
    "El beso también había estado bien."

